  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要一个决策流程图，帮助用户判断什么时候该用持久化图数据库，什么时候用临时图。核心问题是\"Which graph approach should I use?\"，从起点开始分叉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是一个圆角矩形表示用户问题。那第一个判断条件是什么？我假设跟数据规模有关？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start",
        "Size"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一个节点叫Size，判断条件是\"Graph size ≥ 10M nodes/edges?\"，超过一千万就直接走持久化方案。如果规模小，再考虑第二个问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Size",
        "Persistent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Size节点画好了，菱形判断。Yes分支连到Persistent，我标注成\"🏛️ Use Persistent Graphs\"。那小规模数据的第二个判断是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Size",
        "Persistent",
        "Teams"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个判断叫Teams，问题是\"Multiple teams or repeated analysis?\"，如果多团队协作或者需要反复分析，还是走持久化；否则走临时方案。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Teams",
        "Persistent",
        "Transient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
